headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Auto Shop Client Jobs
content: An Auto Shop is more than a front for planning shakedowns with your crew – it is also a legitimate business with a buzzing clientele. Sessanta will get in contact with you when customers pull up with their cars. It’s then up to you to modify them to their specifications and deliver the finished product. Completing any Auto Shop Client Jobs will pay back Double Rewards.
